    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it that it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been my absolute pride and joy, always kept sparkling clean and garaged. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s in truly pristine shape and ready for some new adventures, this is the one for you. Come say hi and take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
