    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle is a rare find for the discerning collector. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster, completely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or blemishes, having been protected by ceramic coating and kept in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and the original scent of the interior remains. Every electronic component and switch functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a meticulous service history with every scheduled maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. The undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork, reflecting its history of fair-weather use only. This is not just a used car; it is a meticulously preserved piece of automotive excellence that drives with the tightness and precision of a brand-new vehicle.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
