    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a total showstopper? I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute gem of a car, and honestly, it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014always garaged, hand-washed only, and the interior still has that fresh new-car smell. You won't find a single scratch or ding on this beauty. It runs like a total dream and is ready for its next big adventure. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to fall in love at first sight!",
