    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This example boasts a pristine chassis with documented subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six delivers linear power through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. Finished in Laguna Seca Blue, the exterior retains its factory luster, while the interior shows negligible bolster wear. Mechanically flawless, this unit features upgraded bushings and a Bilstein PSS10 coilover system for sharpened turn-in response without compromising damping quality. A true turn-key specimen for the discerning collector.",
